high_descs: Turn right and walk to the end of the wooden counter by the door
Pick up the green cup from the counter
Turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink
Wash the cup under water in the sink then remove it
Turn around and walk across the room to the dark cabinet with a microwave on it
Put the cup down on top of the dark cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the washed cup on the dark cabinet

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn right, go forward, then turn right to face the table with the coffee maker.
Pick up the cup from the table, next to the coffee maker.
Turn right, go forward, turn left, go forward, and turn right to approach the sink.
Wash the cup in the sink.
Turn right, go forward, then turn right to approach the counter with the microwave.
Place the cup on the counter with the microwave, on the left front corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cup on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and stand at the end of the wood table with the green cup.
Pick up the green cup from the table.
Go right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the cup in the sink, turn the water on and then off and pick up the cup.
Turn around and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the cup down on the left, front corner of the table with the microwave on it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cup on a table.
